who gets near it.

97
00:09:29,803 --> 00:09:34,183
You can see the roof
is in three levels.

98
00:09:34,261 --> 00:09:37,431
We've named them--
the small one here is Katya.

99
00:09:37,511 --> 00:09:39,641
One thousand roentgen per hour.

100
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:42,640
