102
00:09:44,470 --> 00:09:46,600
Two thousand roentgen.
One hour, fatal.

103
00:09:46,678 --> 00:09:49,848
We used remote-controlled
bulldozers in Afghanistan.

104
00:09:49,928 --> 00:09:53,008
