00:29:27,678 --> 00:29:29,138
(Distant gunshot echoes)

311
00:29:33,094 --> 00:29:35,434
(Dog panting)

312
00:29:35,511 --> 00:29:36,601
(Distant gunshot echoes)

313
00:29:36,678 --> 00:29:38,388
(Panting)

314
00:29:43,803 --> 00:29:45,973
(Muttering):
Go. Go.

315
00:29:46,053 --> 00:29:48,513
Go away. Go!

316
00:29:52,553 --> 00:29:54,683
(Panting)

