00:43:10,261 --> 00:43:12,351
(Dog growling)

463
00:43:15,303 --> 00:43:16,433
-(Gunshot)
-(Dog yelps)

464
00:43:16,511 --> 00:43:18,181
(Dog whimpering)

465
00:43:20,386 --> 00:43:21,676
(Gunshot echoes)

466
00:43:26,845 --> 00:43:28,885
