467
00:43:43,261 --> 00:43:44,681
A lot today.

468
00:43:49,845 --> 00:43:52,005
Where do they get their food?

469
00:43:54,011 --> 00:43:55,891
Bacho:
They eat the chickens.

470
00:43:56,553 --> 00:43:58,513
Then they eat each other.

471
00:44:09,303 --> 00:44:10,893
Door-to-door.

