not being humiliated.

645
00:59:32,553 --> 00:59:35,013
We can make a deal
with the KGB.

646
00:59:35,094 --> 00:59:37,184
You'll leave this information
out in Vienna,

647
00:59:37,261 --> 00:59:40,391
